as stuffing" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">All you need for...</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Christmas planning</h3> </a></article><article id="node-3704711" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-feature node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/feature/christmas-gifts"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/gifts_0.jpg?itok=hMewXj9o" width="468" height="382" alt="a selection of christmas cupcakes" title="Christmas cupcakes" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">All you need for...</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Christmas gifts</h3> </a></article><article id="node-6196701" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-guide node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/howto/guide/christmas-moments-decoration"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/guide/guide-image/2016/11/decorations.jpg?itok=oNdACmAV" width="468" height="382" alt="Christmas decorations" title="Christmas decorations" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Guide</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Christmas decorations</h3> </a></article><article id="node-3665516" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-feature node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/feature/christmas-kitchen"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/feature/feature-hub-image/2013/10/hub-image.jpg?itok=PWaWr80c" width="468" height="382" alt="" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">All you need for...</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Christmas kitchen</h3> </a></article><article id="node-95442" cla